Package: hcc2d-encoder
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: standalone QR and HCC2D PNG encoder
 Single-file C command-line encoder for generating PNG images containing
 standard QR symbols or HCC2D 4-colour and 8-colour symbols.
 .
 It accepts text or file input, supports raw payload encoding or HCC2DF
 payload wrapping, and renders raster output suitable for testing,
 documentation, and reference workflows.
